trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> objects.
This class cannot be inherited.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection"></xref> class.
Appends the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> object to the end of the collection.
The <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> to append to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection"></xref>.
Occurs when the collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> objects is changed.

The <xref:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection.Changed> event occurs when the <xref:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection.Add%2A> method, the <xref:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection.Remove%2A> method, or the <xref:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection.Clear%2A> method is called.
Removes all the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> objects from the collection.
Determines whether the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection"></xref> collection contains a specific <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> object.
The <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding.PropertyName"></xref> of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> to locate in the collection.
`true` if the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> is found in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection"></xref>; otherwise, `false`.

Copies all the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> objects from the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection"></xref> collection to a one-dimensional array, starting at the specified index in the target array.
The zero-based array that receives the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> objects copied from the collection.
The position in the target array at which the array starts receiving the copied items.

Copies all the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> objects from the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection"></xref> collection to a one-dimensional array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> objects, starting at the specified index in the target array.
The zero-based array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> objects that receives the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> objects copied from the collection.
The position in the target array at which the array starts receiving the copied items.
Gets the number of <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> objects in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection"></xref> collection.
The number of <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> objects in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection"></xref>.

Returns an <xref href="System.Collections.IEnumerator"></xref>-implemented object that can be used to iterate through the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> objects in the collection.

An <xref href="System.Collections.IEnumerator"></xref>-implemented object that contains all the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> objects in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection"></xref>.
Gets a value indicating whether the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> objects in the collection can be modified.
`false` in all cases.
Gets a value indicating whether access to the collection is synchronized (thread safe).
`false` in all cases.
Gets an <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> object from the collection with the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding.PropertyName"></xref> value.
The <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding.PropertyName"></xref> of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> to retrieve.

An <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection"></xref> with the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding.PropertyName"></xref>.
Removes the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> object from the collection.
The <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding.PropertyName"></xref> of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> to remove from the collection.
Removes the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> object from the collection.
The <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> to remove from the collection.
Removes the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> object from the collection.
The <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding.PropertyName"></xref> of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> to remove from the collection.
`true` to add the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding"></xref> to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection.RemovedBindings"></xref> collection; otherwise, `false`.
Gets a collection of strings representing the names of bindings that have been removed.
An <xref href="System.Collections.ICollection"></xref> containing the names of bindings that have been removed.
Gets an object that can be used to synchronize access to the collection.
An <xref href="System.Object"></xref> that can be used to synchronize access to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection"></xref>.
